# Project Context Loading

- Read relevant files under `docs/` before changes that touch architecture, API behavior, auth, storage, export, or deployment.
- Do not blindly read every document for small edits; choose the docs that match the task.
- If behavior changes make a document inaccurate, update that document in the same task.
- For Lite package dependency or shared `.stage` compatibility work, also inspect the published/public API expectations in the Lite package docs instead of copying Lite source.
